ed="T" n="0767a01"/><persName key="A010354">釋光瑤</persName>，姓周氏，<placeName key="PL000000003795">北京</placeName>人也。幼鍾荼蓼，都不<lb
ed="T" n="0767a02"/>勝情，誓志出家。捨講肆，入禪林，凡嚮宗<lb
ed="T" n="0767a03"/>師，悉從求益。末遭<persName key="A005612">會禪師</persName>，金<g ref="#CB04280">[鏍-糸+廾]</g><anchor xml:id="beg0767001"/>抉<anchor xml:id="end0767001"/>瞙，明<lb
ed="T" n="0767a04"/>視十方。後到<placeName key="PL000000022054">沂水蒙山</placeName>，結草成庵，怡然宴<lb
ed="T" n="0767a05"/>坐。<placeName key="PL000000020721">鄶</placeName>、<placeName key="PL000000022048">費</placeName>之人翕然從化。時慎邑大夫知重，首<lb
ed="T" n="0767a06"/>創禪宮，次<placeName key="PL000000021539">兗州</placeName>節使<persName key="A010362">王僚</persName>尚書躬請入州行<lb
ed="T" n="0767a07"/>化，奏<anchor xml:id="beg0767002"/>著<anchor xml:id="end0767002"/>額號<placeName key="PL000000021896">寶真</placeName>。學侶憧憧，多霑大利。<date from-iso="0807-02-15" key="j20158562016209" to-iso="0808-02-03">元<lb
ed="T" n="0767a08"/>和二年</date>示滅，享年九十二云。又<placeName key="PL000000027105">唐襄州慈恩<lb
ed="T" n="0767a09"/>寺</placeName><persName key="A010355">釋道堅</persName>，姓王氏，<placeName key="PL000000010986">丹陽</placeName>人也。初發心於<placeName key="PL000000008579">牛頭<lb
ed="T" n="0767a10"/>山</placeName><persName key="A010048">慧忠禪祖</persName>。<date from-iso="0766-12-22" key="j20011912001238" to-iso="0767-02-07">大曆元年</date>，栖隱<placeName key="PL000000016614">池州南泉山</placeName>。後<lb
ed="T" n="0767a11"/>詣<placeName key="PL000000027119">襄漢</placeName>，泊<placeName key="PL000000027105">慈恩寺</placeName>。<date from-iso="0806-01-29" key="j20154742015855" to-iso="0807-02-14">元和初載</date>，相國<ref type="person" target="#A000047">燕公</ref><note resp="sgsz">案《舊唐書．卷十四》：「元和…二年…八月…辛巳…于頔為燕國公。…三年…九月…庚寅，以山南東道節度使于頔守司空、同平章事。」</note>鎮<lb
ed="T" n="0767a12"/>于<placeName key="PL000000027117">漢南</placeName><note resp="sgsz">案《禹貢錐指．卷七》：「『漢南』曰『荆』之義耳。」</note>，深相欽重，問道周勤，施供繁沓。遂<lb
ed="T" n="0767a13"/>於<placeName key="PL000000027088">鳳林關</placeName>外造寺請居。<date from-iso="0807" key="j20158562016209">二年</date>示滅，春秋七<lb
ed="T" n="0767a14"/>十三云。</p>
